            "body": "<p>In my case the following worked: KeyEvent.consume()<\/p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Consumes this event so that it will not be processed in the default manner by the source which originated it. <\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n<p>This stops Windows from stealing my focus, but I'm still able to access my menuitems with the keyboard mnemonics with ALT.<\/p>\n\n<p>Thanks to Scott W for his comment!!<\/p>\n",
